rows.name:
Whew! A Frozen Odifa after a hard
day's work really hits the spot!

rows.label: tlk46500171_02_msg0002
rows.name:
During the day, I'm working on a
sculpture, but I spend the whole time
agonizing over how best to proceed.

rows.label: tlk46500171_02_msg0003
rows.name:
When I was younger, I could decide on a
direction and carve it out in a few short
days, but age does take its toll...

rows.label: tlk46500171_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Why don't you have an Odifa
too? It'll lift your
spirits, I promise you!
